Package: dta
Type: Package
Title: An R Library for Efficient Data Management and Manipulation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("John", "Indika", , "library@stemxresearch.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: John Indika <library@stemxresearch.com>
Description: This package provides simple and efficient tools for data
  management and manipulation, including functions to clean, transform, and
  format datasets using popular data-handling methods. It aims to simplify
  common data-wrangling tasks.
